{"tid":1565722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我痴咗線整咗300個燈籠派俾大家 今晚沙田公園見！","createTime":"2019-09-13T09:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T16:15:30.000Z","uid":319969,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b68bba6a05e4c3103f90c41ee79a4cddf15223e0","tid":1565722,"uid":319969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2icHbVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2icHbVq.jpg&h=1187df9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我用咗3個鐘喺度剪架<br />\n希望大家見到我派都過黎拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想自己拎翻翻屋企咁柒<br />\n你地只係需要撕開雙面膠紙<br />\n再貼就ok喇<br />\n唔識貼可以睇上面張圖<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位有份畫既巴絲<br />\n真係畫得好靚！<br />\n喺學校印嗰陣好多人都問我拎~<br />\n<br />\n利申 啲圖唔係我畫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGS4qiq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGS4qiq.png&h=ecd086b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9.15見！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c65a35ed82477850508bd5080b00c06e80dc6e9d","tid":1565722,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T09:09:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">913中秋要人!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6Tnu54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6Tnu54.jpg&h=d1f0aa7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NBHSAUrkFTtbziGh